msgstr "在平面上的准确匹配"

#: ../source/tutorial/query-a-2d-index.txt:130
msgid ""
"Previously, ``2d`` indexes would support exact-match queries for coordinate "
"pairs."
msgstr "在此之前， ``2d`` 索引支持准确匹配坐标的查询"

